                        <p>* Not yet approved.</p>
                        <p>** 5.3 for supply operations, .5 for grant training.</p>
                        <p>You will note that though matériel grants are phasing out, total
                            assistance has increased through <gloss target="#t_FMS1">FMS</gloss>
                            credits. This is consistent with Taiwan’s continually improving economy,
                            our commitment to the <gloss target="#t_GNP1">GNP</gloss>, and the
                            self-sufficiency aspects of the <persName corresp="#p_NRM1">Nixon</persName> Doctrine.</p>
